## 🧪 Running Tests

```bash
pytest tests/ -v --cov=psat --cov-report=term-missing
```

### Linting

```bash
ruff check psat/
```

---

## 🏗️ Project Structure

```
PSAT/
├── psat/
│   ├── engine.py          # Physics engine (Euler-Maruyama + Numba JIT)
│   ├── visualization.py   # Plotting & animation utilities
│   ├── cli.py             # Command-line interface
│   └── constants.py       # Physical constants (k_B, g, λ_air, e)
├── tests/
│   └── test_physics.py    # Physics accuracy & stability tests
├── app.py                 # Streamlit web UI
├── benchmark.ipynb        # Numba vs Python performance notebook
├── pyproject.toml         # Package config (PEP 517)
└── .github/workflows/
    └── tests.yml          # CI: lint → test → coverage
```

